{"tid":1573502,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"試著説「願榮耀 歸香港」，避免説「香港人加油」","createTime":"2019-09-16T04:23:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T15:03:02.000Z","uid":7971,"like":44,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"793e6a292618d6cfe94c26048cade858571542b1","tid":1573502,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:23:25.000Z","msg":"我知大家要啲互相打氣嘅説話<br />\n但香港人加油 依句野真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n撐警集會 藍絲集會 又係香港人加油<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果真係要打氣 擴大光譜等中老年都可以叫<br />\n不如試下講<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">「願榮耀 歸香港」</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Or<br />\n「願榮耀 歸義士/手足」</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英文口號 可以叫<br />\n「All glory to Hong Kong」<br />\n「All glory to our land/home」"},{"pid":"b0b12c742b76ad5e7089a2af5b6f8ea3625dcbab","tid":1573502,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:23:39.000Z","msg":"自推10"},{"pid":"f64d8c2a80489d9f6130105c6dbedf8ae6fb9c0b","tid":1573502,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:24:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/so4yF19.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fso4yF19.jpg&h=481fa700&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n921民間活動<br />\n下午1:00機場交通壓力測試<br />\n晚上7:00毋忘721元朗恐襲<br />\n928民間活動<br />\n下午1:00機場交通壓力測試<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkpicnic\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkpicnic&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xY429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=fb9c81fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkpicnic</a><br />\n【訂閱野餐頻道】 @hkpicnic<br />\n✅ 接收各種活動資訊<br />\n✅ 如何安全地發夢<br />\n✅ 逃生、自衛等有用貼士"},{"pid":"612590d211b5244da6eb1f17085809332a9e35fd","tid":1573502,"uid":33952,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:25:13.000Z","msg":"嗌香港人加油等同為藍絲同死差佬打氣 只會更加用力扑濕義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid